        Ready to take control of your business?
      </h2>
      <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-xl text-lg leading-8 text-slate-300">
        Join hundreds of stores already using Vendora to streamline their sales, manage inventory, and grow their revenue.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-x-6">
        <a href="/register" class="rounded-md bg-emerald-500 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-emerald-400 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-emerald-500 transition-all">
          Start your 14-day free trial
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-white hover:text-emerald-400 transition-colors">
          Contact Sales <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>